♪ And I hope you're satisfied,
you rascal you ♪

34:21.935 --> 34:23.353
♪ Hey! ♪

34:50.338 --> 34:51.965
Aah!

34:55.176 --> 34:59.347
♪ So you met someone who
set you back on your heels ♪

