43:43.746 --> 43:44.956
♪ He's mine ♪

43:44.997 --> 43:47.041
♪ Wop doo wop
doo wop ♪

43:47.083 --> 43:50.836
♪ Really mine... ♪

43:54.591 --> 43:56.675
Frankie, I want
my money, damn it!

43:59.929 --> 44:01.514
I'll get you, Frankie!

44:01.556 --> 44:03.099
I'll get you!

44:03.141 --> 44:05.351
Frankie, what are you...
Did you go see Zola?!

44:05.393 --> 44:06.978
No! No!
Frankie!

44:07.019 --> 44:08.062
Frankie!

44:08.104 --> 44:10.315
Oh, my god! Frankie!

44:10.356 --> 44:11.899
Frankie, what are you doing?

44:11.941 --> 44:13.901
Frankie, why are you running?

44:13.943 --> 44:15.403
Get him! Get him!

44:15.445 --> 44:16.904
Go! Go!

44:18.823 --> 44:20.575
Frankie, I'm gonna kill you!

44:24.912 --> 44:26.498
Frankie, open the door!

44:26.539 --> 44:27.499
Get in!

44:27.540 --> 44:28.958
Frankie, what is going on?

44:29.000 --> 44:31.002
Shit!

44:31.043 --> 44:32.420
Oh, shit!
Wait a minute!

44:32.462 --> 44:34.255
You ain't got time to say
"hi" to an old friend?

44:34.297 --> 44:35.798
Unh!

44:35.840 --> 44:38.301
Get that motherfucker!
Get that boy!

44:38.343 --> 44:40.428
No!

44:40.470 --> 44:42.472
Leave him alone! Oh!
What y'all doing?!

44:42.514 --> 44:44.641
Unh! Unh!

44:44.682 --> 44:45.808
Unh! Mickey!

44:45.850 --> 44:47.685
